---
import '../styles/global.css';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<html lang="en">

<head>
    <Header />
</head>

<body>
    <main class="layout-main">
        <div class="card centered-card">
            <div class="card-icon-wrapper">
                <m3e-shape name="soft-burst" class="m3e-icon-bg" style="--m3e-shape-container-color:var(--md-sys-color-primary);"></m3e-shape>
                <Icon name="material-symbols:license" class="card-icon-foreground" />
            </div>
            <h1 class="profile-title">copyright & usage</h1>
            <div class="card-article">
                <ul class="profile-description">
                    <li>visuals: <br>all character sprites, gifs, and related visual assets belong to their respective creators: undertale & deltarune © toby fox; sonic the hedgehog © sega corporation; hatsune miku © crypton future media, inc. this is a personal, non-commercial fan site, and no copyright infringement is intended.</li>
                    <li>audio: <br>the track playing in the website is <span><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VviAwr9a6vk" class="btn-footer" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">"deltarhythm - city"</a></span> by <span><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@wavluna" class="btn-footer" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">wavluna</a></span>. it is a cover of "hip shop" from the game <span><a href="https://deltarune.com/" class="btn-footer" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">"DELTARUNE"</a></span>, originally composed by toby fox (administered by <span><a href="https://www.materiamusic.com/" class="btn-footer" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">materia music</a></span>).</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <script>
        import '@m3e/web/shape';
    </script>
</body>

</html>